                                <button data-emoji="ğŸ—¡ï¸" data-title="Dagger" data-stat-type="attack" data-stat-value="2" class="w-full text-center py-1 px-2 bg-black/20 rounded-lg focus:bg-blue-900/50 focus:outline-none transition-colors">ğŸ—¡ï¸ Dagger (+2 ğŸ’¥)</button>
